author: dlr
msg: Merge r16754/r16772/r16790 (the last rev being a one-character
whitespace tweak added at the last minute by me), creating deep copy
svn_client_commit_item2_t.  This is needed to prevent pool-related
scoping segfaults in the Ruby bindings.
Approved by: dlr, djames, lundblad, rooneg, kou

author: dlr
msg: Merge r16725, enabling running autogen.sh with Python < 2.1, in which
the scope of variables within lambda is restricted.  This avoids a
build failure from (only) the scoping differences in Python versions.
Approved by: +1: djames, rooneg, dlr, +0: nori
